                <h1>Understanding Walgreens Background Check Process</h1>
                <p>Walgreens conducts background checks on potential employees to ensure a safe workplace. The process typically includes criminal history, employment verification, and drug screening. Candidates should prepare for this comprehensive check, as it can influence hiring decisions. Understanding Walgreens' policies can help applicants navigate this process smoothly.</p>
